<MELItem itemNbr="23-21-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-23-21-01.1.2-23-21-01">
<Title>Selective Call Function (SELCAL)</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>Alternate Procedures Used</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided alternate procedures are established and used.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Alternate procedures:</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>When HF is required for communication with ATC, a listening watch must be maintained on the relevant HF frequency.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Advise dispatch to indicate SELCAL INOP on the flight plan.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="D" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0">
<Title>Procedures Do Not Require Its Use</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided procedures do not require its use. </Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
</DispatchCondition>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="23-21-01-01">
<Title>Channels</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="5" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>Alternate Procedures Used</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided alternate procedures are established and used.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Alternate procedures:</Para>
<Para>SELCAL has channels to VHF L/C/R and HF L/R. Any operative channels may permit SELCAL use.</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Maintain listening watch as required.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>If both HF channels are inoperative advise dispatch to indicate SELCAL INOP on the flight plan.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="D" nbrInstalled="5" nbrRequired="0">
<Title>Procedures Do Not Require Its Use</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided procedures do not require its use. </Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELSubItem>
</MELItem>
